---
// Down chevron between steps in a track diagram
---
<div class="step-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg width="12" height="10" viewBox="0 0 12 10">
    <use href="#icon-arrow-down" />
  </svg>
</div>

<style>
  .step-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 0 0 5px;
    height: 10px;
    color: var(--color-arrow-muted);
  }
</style>
